            <p>The moment that a stage of the project is complete, a staff member can update the status. Every team member instantly sees the update so everyone stays informed and ahead of the game.</p>
            <h5>Secure Archives</h5>
            <p>All previous jobs and invoices archived in one, easy to access location.</p>
