            <p>Keep all your project scopes in one place. Add details, quotes and files as they arise until a scope becomes a new job.</p>
            <h2>Contacts</h2>
            <h5>Never Lose a Number Again</h5>
            <p>All your contacts in one place. Categorize your staff, contractors, clients and suppliers for convenience.</p>
            <h5>Sharper Communication</h5>
            <p>Invite contacts to one or more jobs and allow them access to all current project information. Information flows effortlessly amongst team members and no time is wasted.</p>
            <h2>Settings</h2>
            <h5>Customize your System</h5>
